checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅ 2 | ❌ 4</summary>\n\n### ❌ Failed checks (3 warnings, 1 inconclusive)\n\n|      Check name     | Status         | Explanation                                                                                                                                                                                          | Resolution                                                                                                                                                                        |\n| :-----------------: | :------------- | :--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | :-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|     Title check     | ⚠️ Warning     | The PR title mentions loading Font Awesome to fix checkboxes, but the actual changes only modify CSS selectors and add styling rules without implementing Font Awesome loading.                      | Update the title to reflect the actual changes made, such as 'Add scoped checklist styling and CSS updates' or verify that Font Awesome loading code is present in the changeset. |\n|  Description check  | ⚠️ Warning     | The description claims Font Awesome injection was added to CodeMirror.tsx, but the provided changeset only shows CSS modifications in checkbox.ts and noteStyle.ts files.                            | Either include the CodeMirror.tsx changes in the PR or revise the description to match the actual CSS-only modifications present in the changeset.                                |\n|  Docstring Coverage | ⚠️ Warning     | Docstring coverage is 50.00% which is insufficient. The required threshold is 80.00%.                                          